---
title: Caribbean Style Spiced Salmon with Kiwi Salsa, Chips and Zesty Slaw
description: This Caribbean Style Spiced Salmon is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
